{{Expand Spanish|date=August 2015|Rogelio Ricardo Livieres Plano}}

'''Rogelio Ricardo Livieres Plano''' (August 30, 1945 &ndash; August 14, 2015) was a Roman Catholic bishop.

Born in [[Argentina]], Livieres Plano was ordained to the priesthood in 1978. In 2004, Livieres Plano was appointed bishop of the Roman Catholic Diocese of Ciudad del Este, [[Paraguay]]. On September 25, 2014, he was removed from office.<ref>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/blivpl.html Rogelio Ricardo Livieres Plano]</ref>

